---
/* Sección de información / Acerca de */
---

<section class="relative py-24 px-4" id="about">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

		<!-- Título de sección -->
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
				¿QUÉ ES <span class="text-cyan">E-SPORTS UNLu</span>?
			</h2>
			<div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan to-orange mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
		</div>

		<!-- Cards -->
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
			<!-- Card 1 -->
			<div class="info-card group">
				<div class="info-card-icon bg-cyan/10 text-cyan group-hover:bg-cyan/20">
					<svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-3">COMPETENCIAS</h3>
				<p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed text-sm">
					Torneos internos y externos en los juegos más populares. Representá a la UNLu en competencias universitarias.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Card 2 -->
			<div class="info-card group">
				<div class="info-card-icon bg-orange/10 text-orange group-hover:bg-orange/20">
					<svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-3">COMUNIDAD</h3>
				<p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed text-sm">
					Conectá con otros gamers de la universidad. Formá equipos, compartí estrategias y hacé amigos.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Card 3 -->
			<div class="info-card group">
				<div class="info-card-icon bg-green-unlu/10 text-green-unlu group-hover:bg-green-unlu/20">
					<svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-3">EVENTOS</h3>
				<p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed text-sm">
					Eventos presenciales y online, streamings en vivo, charlas y actividades para toda la comunidad universitaria.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.info-card {
		position: relative;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.08);
		background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.3);
		backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
		transition: all 0.4s ease;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.info-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		height: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.3), transparent);
		opacity: 0;
		transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
	}
	.info-card:hover {
		border-color: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.2);
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
	}
	.info-card:hover::before {
		opacity: 1;
	}
	.info-card-icon {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 3.5rem;
		height: 3.5rem;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}
</style>
